  "how-to-secure-boot-arch": [
    {
      "id": 90,
      "date": "2021-10-17T22:29:54+08:00",
      "author": "竹林里有冰",
      "url": "https://blog.zhullyb.top",
      "text": "失踪了大半年总算想起来更博了",
      "parent": 0,
      "reply_to": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 91,
      "date": "2021-10-17T22:33:07+08:00",
      "author": "Star_caorui",
      "url": "/",
      "text": "失踪人口回归计划.jpg",
      "parent": 90,
      "reply_to": "竹林里有冰"
    },
    {
      "id": 96,
      "date": "2022-01-30T12:02:16+08:00",
      "author": "Micraow",
      "url": "",
      "text": "用grub引导的机子，要用以下命令重新安装grub\n\n/usr/share/grub/sbat.csv在启用模块的情况下重新安装 GRUB TPM并签名：\n\n# grub-install --target=x86_64-efi --efi-directory=esp --modules=\"tpm\" --sbat /usr/share/grub/sbat.csv\n# sbsign --key MOK.key --cert MOK.crt --output esp/EFI/GRUB/grubx64.efi esp /EFI/GRUB/grubx64.efi\n# cp esp/GRUB/grubx64.efi esp/boot/grubx64.efi\n\nesp是引导器分区，通常是/boot",
      "parent": 0,
      "reply_to": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 97,
      "date": "2022-01-30T12:02:47+08:00",
      "author": "Micraow",
      "url": "",
      "text": "参考archwiki:\n\nhttps://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Unified_Extensible_Firmware_Interface/Secure_Boot",
      "parent": 96,
      "reply_to": "Micraow"
    }
  ],
